---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Camps de Vacances" lang="fr" description="Camps de Vacances à Forest International School Paris - Ouvert à TOUS les enfants !">
  <!-- Hero Section with Image -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="/images/summer-camp.jpg"
        alt="Camps de Vacances à Forest International School"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#1e3d29]/90 to-[#2d5a3d]/70"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#c9a962] text-[#1e3d29] rounded-full font-bold text-sm mb-6">
          OUVERT À TOUS LES ENFANTS
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Camps de Vacances
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8">
          Éveillez la curiosité, la créativité et la connexion avec la nature pendant les vacances scolaires. Aventures pour les 2-12 ans !
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="#camps" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-[#c9a962] text-[#1e3d29] font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-[#d4b872] transition-colors shadow-lg">
            Voir les camps
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/fr/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-white/10 text-white font-bold rounded-full border-2 border-white/30 hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors">
            Contactez-nous
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Open Day Banner -->
  <section class="bg-[#c9a962] py-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-[#1e3d29] text-white rounded-full font-semibold text-sm mb-4">Portes Ouvertes</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29] mb-3">Journée Portes Ouvertes</h2>
      <p class="text-[#1e3d29]/80 text-lg mb-2 font-semibold">7 mars 2026, 10h - 12h30</p>
      <p class="text-[#1e3d29]/70 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Nous vous invitons chaleureusement à notre Journée Portes Ouvertes pour découvrir notre école, rencontrer notre équipe et comprendre ce qui fait de notre école un lieu spécial pour apprendre et grandir.
      </p>
      <a href="https://forms.gle/5Fz3Dve7MHkF8VcV7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 bg-[#1e3d29] text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-[#2d5a3d] transition-colors shadow-lg">
        S'inscrire à la Journée Portes Ouvertes
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Holiday Camps -->
  <section id="camps" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-[#faf8f5]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#2d5a3d]/10 rounded-full text-[#2d5a3d] font-semibold text-sm mb-4">Programmes 2026</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Nos Camps de Vacances</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- Winter Camp -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="md:flex">
            <div class="md:w-2 bg-[#5b8fa8] shrink-0"></div>
            <div class="p-8 lg:p-10 flex-1">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
                <div>
                  <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#5b8fa8]/15 text-[#5b8fa8] rounded-full text-xs font-semibold mb-3">Hiver</span>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Camp de Vacances d'Hiver</h3>
                </div>
                <a href="https://forms.gle/Ca8vPzv12voQLgpM9" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-2.5 bg-[#2d5a3d] text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-[#1e3d29] transition-colors text-sm shrink-0">
                  S'inscrire
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Dans notre Camp d'Hiver, les enfants vivent un programme orienté nature qui encourage la curiosité, la créativité et la connexion avec la forêt.</p>
              <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-sm">
                <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-xl p-4">
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-1">Dates</p>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-[#1e3d29]">23 - 27 février 2026</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-xl p-4">
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-1">Horaires</p>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-[#1e3d29]">Chaque jour 10h - 16h</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-xl p-4">
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-1">Tarif</p>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-[#1e3d29]">380 €/semaine</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-xl p-4">
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-1">Extras</p>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-[#1e3d29]">6 €/déjeuner &middot; Transport dès 25 €/jour</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Spring Camp -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="md:flex">
            <div class="md:w-2 bg-[#7ab648] shrink-0"></div>
            <div class="p-8 lg:p-10 flex-1">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
                <div>
                  <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#7ab648]/15 text-[#5a8a30] rounded-full text-xs font-semibold mb-3">Printemps</span>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Camp de Vacances de Printemps</h3>
                </div>
                <a href="https://forms.gle/6y8k9xULoLzSCt7n7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-2.5 bg-[#2d5a3d] text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-[#1e3d29] transition-colors text-sm shrink-0">
                  S'inscrire
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Célébrez le printemps avec notre camp de vacances plein de fleurs, d'activités amusantes et de nature !</p>
              <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-sm">
                <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-xl p-4">
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-1">Dates</p>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-[#1e3d29]">20 - 24 avril 2026</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-xl p-4">
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-1">Horaires</p>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-[#1e3d29]">Chaque jour 10h - 16h</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-xl p-4">
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-1">Tarif</p>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-[#1e3d29]">425 €/semaine</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-xl p-4">
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-1">Extras</p>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-[#1e3d29]">6 €/déjeuner &middot; Transport dès 25 €/jour</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Summer Camp -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <div class="md:flex">
            <div class="md:w-2 bg-[#c9a962] shrink-0"></div>
            <div class="p-8 lg:p-10 flex-1">
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
                <div>
                  <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#c9a962]/20 text-[#a8872e] rounded-full text-xs font-semibold mb-3">Été</span>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1e3d29]">Camp de Vacances d'Été</h3>
                </div>
                <a href="https://forms.gle/5JfDd3U13ZTYMvK76" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-2.5 bg-[#2d5a3d] text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-[#1e3d29] transition-colors text-sm shrink-0">
                  S'inscrire
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Notre Camp d'Été offre un riche mélange d'activités de plein air, incluant des jeux d'eau dans notre piscine et des moments de détente en forêt à l'ombre des arbres.</p>
              <div class="mb-6">
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-2">Sessions hebdomadaires</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-[#c9a962]/10 text-[#1e3d29] rounded-lg text-sm font-medium">6 - 10 juillet</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-[#c9a962]/10 text-[#1e3d29] rounded-lg text-sm font-medium">13 - 17 juillet (sauf 14)</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-[#c9a962]/10 text-[#1e3d29] rounded-lg text-sm font-medium">20 - 24 juillet</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-[#c9a962]/10 text-[#1e3d29] rounded-lg text-sm font-medium">27 - 31 juillet</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-[#c9a962]/10 text-[#1e3d29] rounded-lg text-sm font-medium">24 - 28 août</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm">
                <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-xl p-4">
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-1">Tarif</p>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-[#1e3d29]">425 €/semaine</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-xl p-4">
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-1">Repas</p>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-[#1e3d29]">6 €/déjeuner, goûters inclus</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-[#faf8f5] rounded-xl p-4">
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-1">Transport</p>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-[#1e3d29]">Dès 25 €/jour</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
